products.title: H&M Blue Denim Jeans
products.description: 5-pocket jeans in rigid cotton denim that feels firm at first but then softens and loosens with wear. Wide leg with a regular fit from the waist to the hip and a straight, wide cut from the thigh to the hem. Regular waist with a zip fly and button. Regular length, designed to hit the top of the foot with little or no stacking. A denim statement that goes the distance.
